<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="28" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="27.[108,1212,1588,1763]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">DIAGNOSIS BASED ON FEMALE (figs. 1, 3, 5, 6): Recognized by the large body size, slender habitus, and brown coloration with contrasting pale yellow veins.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
